{"tid":1127310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK火熱MV遭禁播 理由竟然係…","createTime":"2019-04-27T04:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T16:20:47.000Z","uid":74065,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f134c7018f8aa3d6e48546925546cd68be1af6b","tid":1127310,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190427090653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190427090653&h=6916f38b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係估你唔到！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190427090653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190427090653&h=31085aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Kill This Love》MV嘅點擊已經超過2億5千萬。<br />\n<br />\n紅遍亞洲嘅韓國人氣女團BLACKPINK月頭推出主打歌《Kill This Love》，MV公開發放後喺短短10個鐘頭已經突破2,000萬點擊，依家仲衝破咗2億5千萬點擊，氣勢真係勁到爆！不過有消息指呢個MV會被韓國KBS電視台禁播，一眾粉絲即刻𢱑晒頭，因為呢個MV既冇色情亦冇暴力，完全諗唔到被禁嘅理由？最終公布嘅理由竟然係「違反道路交通管理法」！<br />\n<br />\n睇番個MV內容，粉絲推斷係因為成員Rose喊住揸車仲要冇攬安全帶，加上之後佢再赤腳喺行車路上奔跑，所以「違反道路交通管理法」導致個MV被禁播。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190427090653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190427090653&h=b02d3f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔着鞋喺行車路跑~<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190427090653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190427090653&h=813508f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇攬安全帶~<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190427/photo/bkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190427090653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190427%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190427085048920-0427_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190427090653&h=00106dd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bc0873f874653505d3e1ea611cabd302ffc36b5","tid":1127310,"uid":3405,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"2樣都係衰rose<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc9c33c6f7a5210f2fe0e4c050c8522cf8ca867","tid":1127310,"uid":223790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6acf8c9dcc36a7e2784988868f24e046d0cc6275","tid":1127310,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"old news"},{"pid":"cd8e547b88499f5d8f4f4bb575618225d05666e9","tid":1127310,"uid":94552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"On9 kbs"}]}